##Creating a Menu
1. Click on the Pages tab in the left menu.

    ![Page]({{ images }}Page-Select-Page.png)

2. Click **Add New** at the top

    ![Add New]({{ images }}Page-Add-New.png)

3. Enter Title in English and French

    ![Page Title]({{ images }}Page-Title.png)

4. Enter Content. Use Tabs on the right to toggle English and French. Also note the various formatting options available at the top of the content area. 

    ![Content]({{ images }}Page-Content.png)

5. Enter Extra page settings and save.
 - Template can be used to show different type of pages. ( Full width layout, Contact Page. ETC. )

    ![Save]({{ images }}Page-Settings-Save.png)